Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Hilary Clinton, Eleanor Roosevelt and Abigail Smith
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yjw41
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 19 Jan 1996
The controversy surrounding Hilary Clinton's involvement in the presidency and the actions of Mrs Roosevelt and Mrs Adams, are the subject of a comparison by Alistair Cooke.